messages.content: You are an expert Java code generator. Provide only the code block with a complete method implementation based on the provided goal. Don't write comments.

Create a java class named Plan which implements IPlanBody with only one method called runCode. The function receives a List of Objects representing a $Belief$. The $Belief$ contains a JSONObject (org.json.simple.JSONObject) at index 0. The JSONObject is a List of 'Glasses' with different parameters. Sort the different Objects inside the List by the key 'shape'. The value of the key shape is of type string. Return the sorted List at index 0 in the $Belief$ of Objects.
